msgid "# 逻辑操作"
msgstr "# Logical Operations"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Logical_Ops/index.md:2
msgid ""
"|api|简要说明|\n"
"|--|--|\n"
"|[and](./and.md) | 逻辑与操作 |\n"
"|[or](./or.md) | 逻辑或操作 |\n"
"|[not](./not.md) | 逻辑非操作 |\n"
"|[logical_and](./logical_and.md)| 用于对两个张量进行逐元素逻辑与运算 |\n"
"|[logical_or](./logical_or.md)| 用于对两个张量进行逐元素逻辑或运算 |\n"
"|[not](./not.md) | 将tensor的值按位取反。 |\n"
"|[invert](./invert.md) | 将tensor每个值按比特位进行翻转。 |\n"
"|[lshift](./lshift.md) | 根据给定值 将tensor张量进行左移位。 |\n"
"|[rshift](./rshift.md) | 根据给定值 将tensor张量进行右移位。 |\n"
"|[xor](./xor.md) | 计算两个元素的异或值。 |\n"
msgstr ""
"|api|Brief Description|\n"
"|--|--|\n"
"|[and](./and.md) | Logical AND operation |\n"
"|[or](./or.md) | Logical OR operation |\n"
"|[not](./not.md) | Logical NOT operation |\n"
"|[logical_and](./logical_and.md)| Performs element-wise logical AND on two tensors |\n"
"|[logical_or](./logical_or.md)| Performs element-wise logical OR on two tensors |\n"
"|[not](./not.md) | Bitwise NOT on tensor values. |\n"
"|[invert](./invert.md) | Bitwise invert each value of the tensor. |\n"
"|[lshift](./lshift.md) | Left shift the tensor by a given value. |\n"
"|[rshift](./rshift.md) | Right shift the tensor by a given value. |\n"
"|[xor](./xor.md) | Compute the XOR of two elements. |\n"

